# Features

## Product Management
- Add, update, and remove products.
- Each product can have a name, description, price, and image.

## User Credit System
- Users can purchase credits to spend on products.
- Users can check their current credit balance.
- Admins can top up user credits directly.

## Admin Panel
- Admins can manage user accounts and product listings.
- Ability to view user activity and credit usage.

## Notifications
- Telegram bot sends notifications for user actions such as purchases and credit updates.
- Admins receive alerts for important activities.

## Easy Installation
- A simple `install.sh` script to set up the bot environment on Ubuntu 20.04 LTS.


''''
bash <(curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wayangkulit95/usermanager/main/install.sh)

''''
